// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/msdcRr three directions city grid dense, written 2023 by jt
// variant of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DljBDm three directions city grid patch
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtBBRw three dir grid patches essence
// 2d essence of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DtsBWl three directional grid patches

// Variant of o city grid formed by combination of rectangular grids randomly rotated in three directions
// (using a "hash" pattern instead of the "crossed T" inside the triangle).
// Click to show underlying triangular grid.

// tags: procedural, 2d, rectangles, grid, grid, triangle, triangles, patterns, random, rectangle, barycentric, city, pattern, hex, grids

